Ikhaya e-Chūō-ku, Niigata
Ibanga lokuhamba ngezinyawo ukuya edolobheni lase-Niigata · Furomachi · Indlu yangasese · Umbhede we-Simons · Ukupaka · Ilungele imindeni!I-Old Saito Residence iseduze kakhulu
Itholakala enkabeni ye-Niigata City, le ndlu ise-Furomachi, futhi iqhelelene ngezinyawo nezindawo zokudlela eziningi, izitolo, nezindawo ezihehayo, futhi yakhiwe endaweni ephephile yokuhlala.Ezivakashini, sinomatilasi we-Simmons onekhishi, izitsha zokupheka, izitsha, ifriji, ifriji, i-microwave, umshini wokuwasha nowokomisa izigubhu, ubhavu ongu-1 kanye nendlu yangasese zinikezwa phansi ngayinye, futhi yonke imibhede ifakwe omatilasi be-Simmons.Indlu yonke iyindawo yakho yonke yokuhlala.Isidlo sasekuseni nesidlo sasekuseni sizolungiswa ehhotela, endlini yase-Italy, i-Marco Polo (cishe imizuzu engu-2-3 uhamba ngezinyawo), okuyingxenye yendawo.Uma ulala nemibhede engu-3, umbhede owodwa owusofa, nombhede owodwa owusofa, singanikeza abantu abangaba ngu-1-6.Inani ngosuku labantu abangu-4.Ohambweni lwebhizinisi, uhambo, ukusetshenziswa komndeni, njll., singakujabulela uma ungakusebenzisa ukuze kube lula kuwe.Indawo yokupaka ikhona emotweni eyodwa encane njengegaraji elingaphakathi.Kukhona izindawo zokupaka uhlamvu lwemali ekhokhelwayo eduze komnyango.Izindawo eziheha izivakashi eziseduze: I-Old Saito Mansion, i-Niigata City Art Museum, i-Furomachi Downtown, Beach, njll.Futhi, amabhasi adlula njalo.
Jan 4–11

Article excerpt
Report: Games and Online Video Gain Traction in Education
Nearly half of all teachers — 48 percent — are using games in their instruction now, according to a new Speak Up research report released by Project Tomorrow. That’s more than double the percentage from five years ago (23 amaphesenti angu).
Our take
Ake Play Games!
Okutholakale muva nje lapho Speak Up umbiko ovela Project Kusasa kubonisa ukuthi 48 amaphesenti angu ukusabela bothishela basebentisa imidlalo njengengxenye ye zabo imfundo-up kusuka 23 abangamaphesenti angu eminyakeni emihlanu nje edlule. Uma ungumuntu phakathi 52 amaphesenti angu not yet bawafaka imidlalo zibe ikharikhulamu yakho, lokho ongakhetha ezintsha namathuba zingase zisebenze emakilasini yakho?
Imidlalo avela ngalokungakahleleki eklasini ayimisha; othisha baye bawafaka udlala futhi adlale ngezigaba zabo ukuze kuzuze izizukulwane. Namuhla, Nokho, amathuba ekilasini yokugembula kakhulu landiswa ngenxa ongakhetha ubuchwepheshe ukuthi isukela zokusebenza ngokoqobo virtual augmented. A nezinto eziningi ongakhetha ezikhona, kokubili bendabuko kanye digital, ukuba bakhonze izidingo zihlukahlukene okusekelwe yobudala, yokufunda preference, amabhajethi kanye isikhala.

UPhilip Kotler, omunye wamadoda amadala amakhulu kwezokukhangisa, ubiza le nto Ukukhangisa kwe-3.0. Encwadini yakhe enegama elifanayo, ubhe
... 
 amakhasimende ukuthi askene ikhodi futhi ayiyise ku-Twitter ukuze aveze imibono yawo.
Leli bekuyisu eliyimpumelelo, njengoba bonke abantu bezwa isidingo sokulalelwa nokuzizwa beqondwa.
Isu liholele ekuqoqweni kwedatha enkulu inkampani eyisebenzise kahle ngezindlela ezahlukene ezahlukene:
- Njengengxenye yokumaketha kwabo kwangaphandle, I-Dominos ithenge ezinye zezindawo zokukhangisa ezibiza kakhulu e-United States, okuhlanganisa namabhodi e-Times Square, konke nje ukukhombisa lawa ma-tweets ekh
...
dingeka khona futhi kusinikeze umfutho wokugcina wokuqala inqubo.
Enye yezindlela ezinhle kakhulu zokusheshisa lo msebenzi yile mibuzo emine:
- Singalalela kanjani ngokuzwakalayo?
- Kungani brand yethu ikhona?
- Yini eyenza umkhiqizo wethu ube ngumuntu?
- Ingabe uhlobo lwethu lunesimilo?
Ngokusekelwe ekuzicabangeni nasezingxoxweni ezigxile kule mibuzo, ungangena phakathi kwemingcele nezinqubo zempendulo ezakha isu lomuntu, inkundla, nokuxhumana. Inhlanhla futhi ukhumbule ukuzijabulisa endleleni.

Ngesikhathi uJesu esebenzela eJudiya, wayesebenza obala, kodwa manje, ngisebenza futhi ngikhulume nani ekusithekeni. Abangewona amakholwa abakuboni nhlobo lokhu. Ukusebenza Kwami phakathi kwenu kuqhelile kokwabanye. La mazwi, lezi zinsolo nezahlulelo, kwaziwa yini kuphela, hhayi abanye. Wonke lo msebenzi wenziwa phakathi kwenu futhi uvuleleke kinina kuphela; akekho kulabo abangakholwa owazi ngawo, ngoba isikhathi asikafiki. Laba b
...
wane ezimbili eminyakeni emithathu nengxenye ngesikhathi seminyaka engamashumi amathathu nantathu esenyameni. Lapho uNkulunkulu oze emhlabeni enza umsebenzi Wakhe, uhlale eqeda umsebenzi wezinkulungwane ezimbili zeminyaka noma inkathi yonke eminyakeni embalwa nje. Akachithi sikhathi, futhi akabambezeli; uvele aqoqele ndawonye umsebenzi weminyaka eminingi ukuze uqedeke eminyakeni embalwa futhi emifushane. Lokhu kungenxa yokuthi umsebenzi awenzayo ungukuvula indlela entsha nokuhola inkathi entsha.

Ngokuhamba kwesikhathi wonke umsebenzisi Inthanethi kuba kudingekile ukushintsha ikhodi - kusuka ku-akhawunti yakho ye-e-mail, i-akhawunti e ukuxhumana nomphakathi, Skype noma ICQ. Okubuhlungu nakakhulu le nkinga ngaphambi abasebenzisi ezimnandi zakudala ICQ-isithunywa. Empeleni indlela ushintshe iphasiwedi yakho ku-ICQ, sizokwenza manje nixoxe.
Esanda kutholakala ushintshe iphasiwedi yakho ku-ICQ ngokuqondile ICQ-iklayenti yayingasekho nhlobo indlela yokubaleka. Siyethemba ukuthi umnikazi omush
... 
haliwe ifayela umbhalo futhi ithunyelwe kumnikazi wesayithi. Futhi ungenza nge lutho iphasiwedi.
Futhi manje ngihlale kabanzi sendlela ushintshe iphasiwedi yakho ku-ICQ kwi website esemthethweni isevisi. Ukuze wenze lokhu sidinga ukuya kwiwebhusayithi ICQ - abangamazi: www.icq.com.
Lokhu kuzothatha wena page main wesayithi lapho uzocelwa ukuba ungene ngemvume noma ukubhalisa. Ukuze ungene ku ngezindlela ezimbili:
- faka inombolo izikhala ICQ nephasiwedi kuwo;
- ugcwalise ikheli leposi le-elekhth
...
inombolo yakho yeselula.
- Ukuze afakazele wena awulona irobhothi, sicela ufake umazisi.
- Chofoza amagama "eduze."
- Zonke umsebenzi kwenziwa. Nge-imeyili noma kuselula yakho uzothola i-imeyili yokuqinisekisa. Odinga ukukwenza - ulandele isixhumanisi ku-imeyili, khona-ke ungakwazi ukushintsha iphasiwedi ICQ.
Empeleni, yilokho kuphela. Uma inqubo iphasiwedi ishintsha kuphumelela, uhlelo azokwazisa ngami lokhu athandwayo umyalezo "Iphasiwedi ishintshwe ngempumelelo."

'Akumele babe ngabeSatawu abanodlame'
2012-10-09 14:01
Cape Town - Abashayeli bamaloli abanodlame futhi abanesandla ekufeni komshayeli waseKapa, baphumile esandleni futhi abahambisi ngokwemigomo yenyunyana, kumele babahekane nengalo yomthetho, kusho iSA Trade Transport Workers Union.
"Asicabangi ukuthi abantu abanjalo bayingxenye yentando yeningi esihambisa ngayo, akusibo abeSatawu," kusho umkhulumeli wenyunyana uVincent Masoga.
Umshayeli weloli uGary Stewart, 41, wajikijelwa ngetshe eselolini, ubexhunywe
imishini emsiza ukuba akwazi ukuphefumula, kulandela ukuthi elimale
kambi ekhanda, wase efelwa wumqondo.
Abasebenzi ababesesitelekeni, okuyibo abajikijela uStewart, kuthiwa ngabenyunyana iSatawu.
"Akekho umuntu ongaphansi kweSatawu ongenza lolu dlame," kusho uMasoga.

The mixers are widely used in pharmaceutical, food, dye, feed, chemical fertilizer and pesticide industries and especially suitable for mixing various solid materials with large volumed ,000 to 12,000 litres).
The mixing barrel swings while rotates so that the materials in the barrel can be fully mixed. Because the discharge port of the barrel is out of the barrel centreline, the mixer features quick mixing and discharging, as well as high volume mixing capacity.
Eyh Series ezimbili mixer ntathu ikakhulu siqukethe izingxenye ezintathu: Rotor sigubhu, yokubeka liyaphambuka futhi uzimele. I-drum Rotor amanga liyaphambuka yokubeka, kusekelwa amasondo amane kanye Axial yayo nenkanuko edlulele kwenziwa namasondo amabili chock. Amabili amasondo amane eliqhutshwa ujikelezisa amandla uhlelo ukwenza Phendula isilinda. I yokubeka liyaphambuka is eliqhutshwa iqoqo crankshaft ibha oscillating okuyinto ogibele Uhlaka kanye wahosha yokubeka isekelwa uzimele.
Lolu dengezi ligijima of Eyh ezimbili mixer ntathu kungaba siya ezimbili isiqondiso ngesikhathi esifanayo. Esinye sazo ukujikeleza drum kanye nezinye is wahosha of sigubhu eduze yokubeka liyaphambuka. Izinto okwakumelwe zixutshwe uzobe ijikelezwe lapho imigqomo is ligijima, futhi ngeke zixutshwe kwesokudla noma kwesokunxele uma uMbhalo is wahosha. Ngenxa yalokho lezi iminyakazo ezimbili, izinto kungenziwa exutshwe ngokugcwele ngesikhathi esifushane. Eyh mixer ezimbili ntathu kufanelekile ukuxuba ubhuqu granule ukuma izinto.

Umongameli Mokgweetsi Masisi wakwele Botswana wethule amazwi akhe enduduzo phezu kokutshona kowayengumongameli weZimbabwe, uMnumzana Robert Mugabe, ngokuloba amazwi akhe ebhukwini lenduduzo ehofisini yommeli weZimbabwe kweleBotswana, ngoLwesine.
Umongameli Masisi ulobe amazwi akhe awenduduzo kubhuku elivulwe ngoMvulo, ukuze abantu bakhale kanye lemuli yeZimbabwe.
UMasisi uchaze umuyi uMnumzana Robert Mugabe njengomuntu owachitha isikhathi eside elwela inkululeko yabantu beZimbabwe. Uthi kunengi okuhlanganisa eleBotswana kanye leleZimbabwe.
"Sikhala labo. Sikhala labo ngokulahlekelwa ababhekane lakho. Sijabulela impilo asiphe yona, noma nje kwakunzima ngoba isikhathi eside usichithe esempini. Yimpilo ebilempumela, impilo emabalabala. Impilo kamongameli Mugabe," kutsho umongameli Masisi.
Ummeli weZimbabwe kweleBotswana uMnumzana Henry Mukonoweshuro ubonge ukusekelwa ngumongameli Masisi ngalesi isikhathi.
Kodwa abanye abeZimbabwe abahlala kweleBotswana, abafana lo Mnumzana Andreas Sibanda bathi uMugabe watshiya kunambitha okumnandi kanye lokubabayo emlonyeni ngesikhathi sombuso wakhe.
Umongameli Masisi uthi eleBotswana lizathumela iqula eliphezulu, eligoqela umsekeli wakhe, uMnunzana Slumber Tsogwane kanye lowayengumongameli wakuqala weleBotswana, uMnumzana Festus Mogae eZimbabwe ukuyavalelisa umufi.

I-Hardware Libre yiphrojekthi enikezelwe ekusabalaliseni mayelana nobuchwepheshe obusha be-Open Hardware. Eziningi ezaziwa ngokuthi i-Arduino, Raspberry kepha ezinye hhayi njenge-FPGAs. Singabanethiwekhi ye-blog ye- Ibhulogi yezindaba esebenza kusukela ngo-2006.
Ngo-2018 sibe ngozakwethu be- Mahhala nge omunye wezehlakalo ezibaluleke kakhulu zaseSpain ezihlobene nokunyakaza kwamahhala nokuvulekile, kokubili ku-Hardware naku-Software
Ithimba lokuhlela le-Hardware Libre lakhiwa iqembu labenzi, ongoti ku-Hardware, electronics kanye nobuchwepheshe. Uma nawe ufuna ukuba yingxenye yeqembu, unga sithumele leli fomu ukuze sibe ngumhleli.

Awukho umsebenzi ozokuvumela ukuthi udube i-Photoshop njengochwepheshe. I-Photoshop Elements iyinhlekisa ngoba akusona ngisho nesakhiwo sokufunda i-Photoshop. Okufanayo kuya ku-Office. Lokho okushiwo, ngaphandle kokuthi umpofu, akufanele uhambe uzungeze isofthiwe engu-$1-$50.
Ingabe i-Adobe CC ingagqekezwa?
Uhlelo olusha lwe-Adobe lokuhlela isithombe oludidiyelwe ngamafu lwe-Photoshop CC luphangwe lungakapheli usuku lukhishwe. … Njengoba i-Fstoppers ibika, amakhophi e-software abiwe abiwa nge-Bi
... 
iso ze-GIMP. Zombili izinhlelo zisebenzisa amaCurves, Levels kanye Nemaski, kodwa ukukhohlisa kwe-pixel yangempela kunamandla ku-Photoshop.
Yini ongayisebenzisa esikhundleni se-Photoshop?
Ezinye izindlela zamahhala ze-Photoshop
- I-Photopea. I-Photopea ingenye yamahhala ku-Photoshop. …
- I-GIMP. I-GIMP inika abaklami amandla ngamathuluzi okuhlela izithombe nokudala ihluzo. …
- I-PhotoScape X. …
- I-FireAlpaca. …
- I-Photoshop Express. …
- UPolarr. ...
- UKrita.
Ingabe i-Photoshop ayikho emthethw
...
lelo zokusebenza ezibusa ngendlela efanayo kweminye imikhakha, kusho i-AutoCAD yabadwebi bezakhiwo nonjiniyela, zibiza amakhulukhulu amadola ngenyanga.
Ingabe kukhona ukuthenga ngesikhathi esisodwa kwe-Photoshop?
Uma ufuna ukwazi ukwenza ukuhlela okungahleliwe ezithombeni ngokuzayo ngaphandle kokukhokhela ukubhalisa noma ukubhalisa kabusha njalo uma ufuna ukuhlela izithombe, uzodinga ukuthenga inguqulo ezimele ye-Photoshop. Nge-Photoshop Elements, ukhokha kanye futhi ube ngumnikazi wayo phakade.

Impendulo YeBhayibheli
Ukuthula emhlabeni kuzoba khona, ngoMbuso kaNkulunkulu, uhulumeni wasezulwini obuswa uJesu Kristu, hhayi ngemizamo yabantu. Phawula indlela iBhayibheli elisifundisa ngayo ngaleli themba elimangalisayo.
UNkulunkulu ‘
uyoqeda izimpi kuze kube semkhawulweni womhlaba,
’ egcwalisa isithembiso sakhe sokuletha ‘ukuthula emhlabeni kubantu abathokozelwa nguye!
’—IHubo 46:9; Luka 2:14, iBhayibheli lesiZulu elivamile.UMbuso kaNkulunkulu uyobusa umhlaba wonke usezulwini. (Daniyeli 7:14) Njengohulumeni womhlaba, uyoqeda ubuzwe obuyimbangela yezingxabano eziningi.
UJesu, uMbusi woMbuso kaNkulunkulu, ubizwa ngokuthi “
iSikhulu Sokuthula,
” futhi uyoqikelela ukuthi ‘ukuthula ngeke kuphele.
’—Isaya 9:6, 7.Abantu abazimisele ukuqhubeka nempi ngeke bavunyelwe ukuba baphile ngaphansi kwalo Mbuso ngoba “
ngokuqinisekile umphefumulo [kaNkulunkulu] uyamzonda umuntu othanda ubudlova.
”—IHubo 11:5; IzAga 2:22.UJehova ufundisa izikhonzi zakhe indlela yokuphila ngokuthula. Lichaza imiphumela yale mfundo, iBhayibheli lithi: “
Ziyokhanda izinkemba zazo zibe ngamageja nemikhonto yazo ibe ngocelemba. Isizwe ngeke sisaphakamisela isizwe inkemba, futhi ngeke zisayifunda impi.
”—Isaya 2:3, 4.
Kumanje izigidi zoFakazi BakaJehova emhlabeni wonke zifunda kuNkulunkulu indlela yokuba nokuthula. (Mathewu 5:9) Nakuba sivela ezizindeni ezihlukahlukene futhi sihlala emazweni angaphezu kuka-230, siyenqaba ukuya empini.

Sihle Ndlovu
IKaizer Chiefs ivume icala yase ihlawuliswa imali encane ngesenzo sayo sokungayidlali imidlalo emibili ngoDisemba.
Lokhu kuqinisekiswe umshushisi wePremier Soccer League (PSL) uZola Mavaju ngoLwesibili. UMajavu uthe sekuphele nya ngalolu daba.
“Ngingakuqinisekisa ukuthi iKaizer Chiefs ivelile phambi kwekomiti eliqondisa ubugwegwe ngoLwesibili ukuzophendula mayelana nokungayidlali imidlalo emibili ngoDisemba,” kusho uMajavu esitatimendeni.
“Leyo yimidlalo eyayimbandakanya iCape Town City neLamontville Golden Arrows.”
IChiefs iyidlalile le midlalo emibili yashaywa kuyona yomibili yase ihoxisa indaba yokulwa nePSL ngoba vele bese singekho isidingo.
“IChiefs ilivumile icala ngase ngikwamukela lokho, okuholele ekutheni iPSL ithathe isinqumo. IChiefs ihlawuliswe u-R200 000 kanti uhhafu wale mali ulengisiwe kuze kube ayitholakali inecala elifanayo esikhathini esiyizinyanga ezingu-12.
“Lokhu kuchaza ukuthi kumele bakhokhe u-R100 000. Okwesibili okumele bakwenze ukuthi bakhokhe izindleko zokuhlalelwa kwecala okuzohlelwa kahle yiligi bese ihambisa konke kubona. Leli cala seliphelile nya.”

Izivumelwano ezihlanganyelwe: imuphi umholo wabasebenzi abasemaholidini okubeletha?
Ikhefu lokuyoteta linomthelela eholweni lomsebenzi. Mayelana nalokhu, isivumelwano esisebenza ngokubambisana singase sidinge umqashi ukuthi anakekele iholo lakhe.
Umbuzo bese uqhamuka wokuthi yiziphi izakhi zomholo okufanele zigcinwe ngalesi sikhathi, futhi ikakhulukazi amabhonasi nezinye izipho.
Lapha, konke kuncike esimweni se-premium. Uma kuyibhonasi inkokhelo yayo ehambisana nemibandela yokuba khona, ukungabibikho komsebenzi osekhefini lokuyoteta kugunyaza umqashi ukuthi angamkhokheli. Umbandela owodwa, nokho: konke ukungabikho, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi imvelaphi yakho, kufanele kubangele ukungakhokhwa kwale bhonasi. Uma kungenjalo, umsebenzi angase afune ukucwaswa ngenxa yokukhulelwa kwakhe noma ukubeletha kwakhe.
Uma ukukhokhwa kwebhonasi kuncike ekusebenzeni komsebenzi othile, futhi, umqashi angeke amkhokhele umsebenzi ngekhefu lokuyoteta. Qaphela kodwa ngoba amajaji aqinile kulolu daba.

Isitimela sezingane sangaphandle esisikhiqizayo siyisitimela esiklanyelwe izingane ngokukhethekile. Isitimela asiphephile nje kuphela, kodwa futhi sinezinhlobonhlobo zezindikimba. Ezinganeni, into yokuqala ezihehayo wukubukeka kohambo lwesitimela, okuyindikimba yesitimela. Amatimu ahlukahlukene angaheha izingane kakhulu. Into yokuqala abazali okufanele bayicabangele ukuthi ukugibela kwezingane ngaphandle kwesitimela kuphephile yini. Ezinganeni ezincane ezingenakho ukuqwashisa ngokuphepha, lapho zithatha uhambo lwesitimela, into ebaluleke kakhulu ukuqinisekisa ukuphepha kwazo. Ngale njongo, siklame ngokukhethekile amabhande aphephile, angengezwa ohambweni lwesitimela lwangaphandle oluthengiswa e-Dinis. Uma ufuna ukuphepha okwengeziwe kwezingane isitimela sangaphandle, ungakhetha ukwengeza amabhande aphephile. Sikholelwa ukuthi isitimela sangaphandle esinosayizi wengane esithengiswayo e-Dinis siyisinqumo sakho esingcono kakhulu.

i-grep ingenye yamathuluzi asetshenziswe kakhulu kulayini womyalo we-GNU / Linux. Yize ulithuluzi elilula kakhulu, likuvumela ukuthi wenze imisebenzi eminingi. Isetshenziswa ikakhulukazi ngokuhlangana namapayipi, ukuthola amaphuzu athile ekukhishweni komyalo wangaphambilini, njll. Kepha kukhona futhi ithuluzi elaziwa njenge-egrep elilingana nokusebenzisa i-grep ngenketho ye -E.
I-e ivela ku "Regex enwetshiwe", okuyiyona eyenza kusebenze inketho ye -E nokuthi yini onayo ku-egrep ngokuzenzakalela 
... 

Kepha uma uzibuza ngomehluko nge-grep, nasi isibonelo esizokucacisela ... Esimweni sokusebenzisa i-grep ngaphandle -E kufanele usebenzise i- ukulandelana kokuphunyuka ukuze ihumushe abalingiswa abakhethekile kanjalo, ngaphandle kwalokho ibingahumusha iphethini kanjalo ngaphandle kokubheka. Ngakolunye uhlangothi, nge-egrep noma i-grep -E kuzobacabangela. Ngokwesibonelo:
grep '^no\(fork\|group\)' /etc/group
Lokho kungalingana no:
grep -E '^no(fork|group)' /etc/group
egrep '^no(fork|group)' /etc/g
...
unikeza imininingwane engadingekile futhi kungadida, ikakhulukazi kulabo abangenalo ulwazi lwe-GNU namathuluzi anamandla elinikezayo.
Ekugcineni, ungeze futhi walungisa isiphazamisi engisibonisile ngemuva kokuphawula kwami kokuqala (^ $). Njengakwezinye izingosi, bekufanele ngabe ucaphune umuntu olungisile, noma okungenani uthi ukulungiswa, okuyingxenye yesisekelo se-GNU, isisekelo esifanayo nale blog esiqale ngaso futhi esenziwe ngaso elahlekile.
A ukubingelela.
Ngiyabonga ngombono wakho.

Ngokomchazampilo wengqamuzana, Ingqimbazana ibizo elibhekisela kuzo zonke izithako ezingaphakathi kwengqamuzana lemvelendeni, elingungwe ulwelwesi lwengqamuzana, ngaphandle kwendeni yengqamuzana. Izithako ezingaphakathi kwendeni neziqukethwe ulwelwesi lwendeni zona zibizwa ngokuthi isicabandeni (nucleoplasm). Izigcoyi eziyinhloko zengqimbazana ziyintikicana (cytosol) (isiqa esintikintiki), izithokazane (organelles) (izinhlaka zengqamuzana ezingaphakathi), kanye nezinye izithako ezakha ingqamuzana. Ingqimbazana ngokwayo ingamanzi angama-80 ekhulwini futhi imvama ayinambala. Imisebenzi eminingi ebalulekile yengqamuzana yenzeka kwizithokazane, ezifana nezinsimbi zenguxa yokwenza imisebenzi eminingi.
Intikicana iqukethe ingxube eyinkimbinkimbi yemicu yesixhakangqamu, kufaka phakathi i-endoplasmic reticulum kanye nezinto zikaGolgi. Kubandakanya nemizwayi encibilikisiwe, namanzi agcwalisa ingxenye enkulu yengqamuzana. Ngenxa yalolu xhoxho lwemicu, ulwelwesi nemizwayikhulu emaningi encibilikile njengezakhamzimba, intikicana ayisebenzi njengoketshezi olulula. Umsebenzi oyinhloko wengqimbazana ukubamba izithokazane endaweni.

Sizokhuluma ngalezi nezinye izifiso kule ndatshana. Thola okuningi ngale sizini esisanda kuyiqala.
Inkomba
Kungani umoya wenza umsindo?
Ezinsukwini eziningi zasebusika - futhi, empeleni, unyaka wonke - umoya ungashaya kanzima. Ngokwenza njalo, uma uhlangabe
... 
ngabonakali, kunencazelo yesayensi, futhi yilokhu: amakhekheba eqhwa, akhiwa amakristalu eqhwa, abamba umhwamuko wamanzi lapho ewa, futhi lowomphunga uphenduka iqhwa. Ukudlula kusuka esimweni segesi (umhwamuko wamanzi) kuya esiqinile (iqhwa) kukhipha ukushisa.
Kungani ubusuku obusika obucacile bubanda kangaka?
Uma uthanda isayensi yezinkanyezi, uqinisekile ukujabulela isibhakabhaka esihle kakhulu sasebusika. Acacile, abukeka ehlanzekile, ... kodwa kubanda ngendlela emangalisayo. Kungani? Ngoba a
...
a okushisayo ukubanda noma ukushisa esikubonayo kungakhathalekile ukushisa kwangempela. Lo mehluko oshisayo phakathi kwesikhumba nendawo ezungezile unqunywa umswakama ozungezile, isivinini somoya nesiqondiso, ukusibekela kwamafu, phakathi kwabanye. (uzothola eminye imininingwane ku- Lesi sihloko). Ngakho-ke, ngokwesibonelo, uma i-thermometer ikhombisa u-10ºC, isibhakabhaka sicacile futhi akukho moya ovunguzayo, sizozwa ukubanda okuncane, 7,5ºC.

I-cycloastragenol powder (78574-94-4) ividiyo
I-cycloastragenol powder Siziqu
Uhlolojikelele
ICycloastragenol iyisithako sokudla esidala sokulwa nokuguga emakethe. Ibuye isetshenziswe ngamafomula ama-skincare nama-cosmetics. ICycloastragenol yaqala ukuthengiswa ku-supplements yokudla e-USA ngonyaka we-2007 ngaphansi kwegama le-TA-65, yingakho i-TA 65 noma i-TA65 iseyigama elijwayelekile kakhulu le-cycloastragenol.
Kuyini uCycloastragenol?
ICycloastragenol imolekyulu etholakala ku-Astragalus memb
... 
a i-telomerase futhi ivumele i-proteinase yenuzi ukuthi ibangele ukwanda nokukhula kwe-telomere DNA.
I-cycloastragenol kanye nokulwa nokuguga
Ukulwa nokuguga yinzuzo ebonakalayo kakhulu ye-cycloastragenol. I-cycloastragenol ayigcini nje ukubambezela ukuguga kwabantu, kodwa ngaphezu kwalokho ithuthukise ukungatheleleki, ubuthi obusongela umkhondo, ukuvikela amaseli enhliziyo, ikakhulukazi okususelwa ku-hydragaloside (Astragaloside Ⅳ) hydrolysis.

... 
engameli wethu. Eqenjini likabani lona? Hheyi asekhohliwe ukuthi umfo kaBhembe kade kwasa ehuzuka kwezepolitiki. Unina kaKhama Billiat, uRosa, ukhulume ngokweseka ukubuyela kwendodana yakhe ekhaya izodlala kwiCastle Lager Premier Soccer League (PSL).
Okujabulisa uRosa kakhulu wukuthi manje usengahambela imidlalo yendodana yakhe ayibuke bukhoma.
Lo mdlali owake wagijima kwi-Ajax Cape Town, Mamelodi Sundowns neKaizer Chiefs ujoyine iYadah Stars ngaphambi kokuqala kwesizini yePSL ka-2024.
Lokhu yinto eyenzeke bembalwa abebeyilindele njengoba bekusenamaqembu ambalwa amfunayo kwiDStv Premiership eNingizimu Afrika.
Ekhuluma nabe-@zimcelebs_official kwi-Instagram, unina kaKhama uthe ujabule ngokuthi ekugcineni usezokwaze ukubuka bukhoma indodana yakhe idlala.
“Kuyinjabulo ukuthi manje usebuyile ekhaya, futhi singambona edlala,” kusho uRosa.
“Besijwayele ukumbona edlala kumabonakude, nangesikhathi sivakashele eNingizimu Afrika.
“Kufanelekile ukuba umama abe seduze nendodana yakhe, futhi njengawo wonke umama, ngiyakujabulela ukuthi indodana yami isayine kwi-Yadah, futhi isibuyile ekhaya.”
Ukubuyela kukaBilliat kwiPremier League akubanga nesiqalo abesifisa njengobabiYadah ihlulwe ngo 1-0 yiHwange emdlalweni wayo wokuqala.
UBilliat ungene esuka ebhentshini emizuzwini engu-15 yokugcina kodwa akazange akwazi ukujika izinto zivune iMiracle Boys.

Genevieve Quintal, News24

Jonas useqinisekisile ukuthi umndeni wezinjinga wakwaGupta wamenzela isiphakamiso
sokuthi abe ngungqongqoshe.
"Umndeni wakwaGupta wangenzela isiphakamiso sokuthi
ngingene esikhaleni sikaNhlanhla Nene,” esho esitatimendeni ngoLwesithathu.
"Nganqaba lesi siphakamiso
sengisiphethe ngesandla. Ngabanikeza isizathu esithi uma ngamukela lesi sikhundla
kuyosho ukuthi ngihlekisa ngentando yeningi esayilwela kanzima.
“Ngokwami ngazi ukuthi akekho omunye umuntu onelungelo
lokuqoka ongqongqoshe ngaphandle kukamengameli wezwe.”
OLUNYE UDABA: Ungazi kahle kamhlophe uZuma - Mentor
Imibiko yavela
ngempelasonto yokuthi uJonas wabizelwa emhlanganweni okwakukhona kuwo
abakwaGupta wase “enikezwa” lo msebenzi emasontweni amabili andulela ukhishwa
esikhundleni kukaNene.
Iphephandaba iSunday Times laphinde labika ukuthi
indodakazi kaMengameli Jacob Zuma, uDuduzane, wayekhona kulo mhlangano ehhotela
eliseSandton ngoNovemba.
Iphephandaba laqhuba ngokuthi uJesse Duarte wabe esenza
lesi siphakamiso kuJonas ngemuva kwezinsuku ezimbili.
Nokho, uJonas uphikile ukuthi uDuarte weza kuye
nesiphakamiso somsebenzi.

Iyiphi inkampani yokubamba i-Zinc alloy eyenza i-OBM?
I-SHANGHAI HENGCHUAN HARDWARE Co., Ltd. izinikele ekubeni ngomunye wabakhiqizi abahamba phambili be-OBM yesibambo se-Zinc alloy esezingeni eliphakeme. Sizobhekana nakho konke...
I-SHANGHAI HENGCHUAN HARDWARE Co., Ltd. izinikele ekubeni ngomunye wabakhiqizi abahamba phambili be-OBM yesibambo se-Zinc alloy esezingeni eliphakeme. Sizoba nesibopho sayo yonke into efana nokukhiqiza nokuthuthukiswa, uchungechunge lokuhlinzeka, ukulethwa, nokuphromotha. Uma unokuthile okucacisiwe kanye nesithombe noma isampula, sicela uthumele imininingwane sizothuthukisa imikhiqizo ngokwesidingo sakho.
Kanye nenzuzo enkulu yomthamo omkhulu, i-SHANGHAI HENGCHUAN HARDWARE yandisa isilinganiso sayo sokukhiqiza ukuze yanelise izidingo eziphakeme zesibambo sengxube ye-Zinc. Njengolunye lochungechunge lwemikhiqizo eminingi ye-Hench, uchungechunge lwe-Soft Closing Drawer Slide lujabulela ukuqashelwa okuphakeme kakhulu emakethe. I-Hench Hinge iklanywe ngokunembile ochwepheshe bethu besebenzisa umqondo wakamuva wokuklama. Umkhiqizo ngeke uphele kalula. Akulula ukulahlekelwa ubusha noma ukucwebezela kombala lapho uchayeka elangeni elinamandla.
Silwela ikusasa elisimeme. Imibandela eqinile yezemvelo nenhlalo isetshenziswa kuwo wonke amazinga okukhiqiza, kusukela ekutholeni impahla eluhlaza kuye ezigabeni zokukhiqiza ezilandelayo, kuze kufike ekulebulweni komkhiqizo osuphelile.

Siyaxolisa kakhulu ngodaba lwakamuva olushicilelwe yi Impempe.com mayelana nezinsolo ezibhekiswe kumengameli weKZN Athletics, uSteve Mkasi.
Inhloso yethu ngokubika ngalolu daba bekuwukuveza izinsolo ezibucayi futhi sithwese abasezikhundleni ijoka lokuziphendulela.
Nokho-ke siyaqonda ukuthi indlela udaba olwethulwe ngayo kungenzeka idale usizi nokuphatheka kabi kuMnu Mkasi nabanye.
Siyavuma ukuthi wonke umuntu unelungelo lokuthathwa njengomuntu omsulwa aze atholwe enecala, futhi siyazisola ngobubi ukubika kwethu okungase kubudale esithunzini sikaMnu uMkasi.
Njengomthombo wezindaba ozibophezele ekubikeni iqiniso ngokungesabi, sizobe sibuyekeza izinqubo zethu zokuhlela ukuze siqinisekise ukuthi ukubika okuzayo ngezindaba ezibucayi kuphathwa ngokucophelela okukhulu.
Kungukuzibophezela kwethu ukuhlinzeka ngobuntatheli obuthembekile nobungenzeleli, obusiza abafundi bethu nomphakathi wonkana.
Sizolwela ukugcina izinga eliphakeme lokubika ngokuziphatha kuyo yonke imizamo yethu yesikhathi esizayo.
Siyaphinda futhi, sidlulisa ukuxolisa kuMnu. Mkasi nakubo bonke abafundi bethu nganoma yiluphi usizi oludalwe wukubika kwethu. Siyabonga ngokuqonda kwakho.
Ozithobayo,
Ithimba labahleli be-Impempe.com

Cha. Alikho igama elithi “isihlanzo” eBhayibhelini noma imfundiso yokuthi imiphefumulo yalabo asebafa iya esihlanzweni ukuze bahlanzwe. * Qhathanisa lokho okufundiswa iBhayibheli ngesono nokufa, nalokho okushiwo imfundiso yokuthi kukhona isihlanzo.
Akuyona indawo yesihlanzo esusa izono zethu, kodwa igazi likaJesu nokuba nokholo kuye. IBhayibheli lisitshela ukuthi “igazi likaJesu iNdodana [kaNkulunkulu] lisihlanza kuso sonke isono,” nokuthi ‘uJesu Kristu wasikhulula ezonweni zethu ngegazi lakhe.’ (1 Johane 1:7; IsAmbulo 1:5) UJesu wanikela ngokuphila kwakhe ‘kwaba yisihlengo sabaningi’ ukuze kuhlanzwe izono zabo.—Mathewu 20:28.
Abantu abafile abezwa lutho. “Abaphilayo bayazi ukuthi bayokufa; kodwa abafileyo bona abazi lutho.” (UmShumayeli 9:5) Uma umuntu eseshonile akabe esezwa lutho, ngakho asikho isihlanzo noma umlilo ongasusa izono zakhe.
Uma umuntu esefile akabe esajeziselwa izono azenzile. IBhayibheli lithi “inkokhelo yesono ngukufa” futhi “lowo ofile ukhululiwe esonweni sakhe.” (Roma 6:7, 23) Isijeziso esiphelele sesono ukufa.

Lolu hlelo luphinde luhlinzeka umkhandlu omusha ngolwazi olubalulekile lokuqondisisa mayelana nesimo sezimali zikamasipala, ukuhlinzekwa kwezidingongqangi kanye nemiklamo emikhulu, nezindaba ezibalulekile okufanele zidingidwe.
Lo mhlangano uyithuluzi eliwumhlahlandlela wokusiza amakhansela ukuthi akwazi ukwenza imisebenzi yawo ngempumelelo, ehlonipha izimiso ze-Batho Pele wokubeka Abantu Kuqala

I-PSE (Ukuphepha Komkhiqizo Kokusebenza Kukagesi Nento) uhlelo oluyimpoqo lwesitifiketi eJapan. Kubizwa nangokuthi 'Ukuhlolwa Kokuhambisana' okuyisistimu yokungena emakethe ephoqelekile yezinto ezisebenza ngogesi. Isitifiketi se-PSE sakhiwe izingxenye ezimbili: i-EMC nokuphepha komkhiqizo futhi futhi kuwumthethonqubo obalulekile womthetho wezokuphepha waseJapan wezinto ezisebenza ngogesi.
Ukuhunyushelwa kwe-METI Ordinance Yezimfuneko Zobuchwepheshe (H25.07.01), Isithasiselo 9, Ama-lithium ion amabhethri wesibili
● Izinsiza ezifanelekayo: I-MCM ifakwe izinsiza ezifanelekile ezingafinyelela kuwo wonke amazinga we-PSE wokuhlola nokwenza izivivinyo kufaka phakathi ukuphoqelelwa kwangaphakathi kwesifunda njll. Kusenza sikwazi ukuhlinzeka ngemibiko ehlukene yokuhlola eyenziwe ngendlela ye-JET, TUVRH, ne-MCM njll. .
● Ukwesekwa kwezobuchwepheshe: I-MCM ineqembu labachwepheshe labanjiniyela bezobuchwepheshe abali-11 abakhethekile emazingeni nasemithethweni yokuhlola ye-PSE, futhi iyakwazi ukunikeza imithethonqubo nezindaba zakamuva ze-PSE kumakhasimende ngendlela eqondile, ephelele futhi esheshayo.
● Isevisi ehlukahlukene: I-MCM ingakhipha imibiko ngesiNgisi noma ngesiJapane ukuhlangabezana nezidingo zamakhasimende. Kuze kube manje, i-MCM isiqede amaphrojekthi we-PSE angaphezu kwama-5000 kumakhasimende esewonke.

Indwangu kakotini eyenziwe ngezinto ezingavuthiwe zikakotini ingenye yezinto ezibalulekile ekukhiqizeni izingubo.I-150GSM esiyisebenzisayo iyisisindo sakudala kakhulu ku-cotton twill, futhi umuzwa wabo othambile kanye nokucwebezela okuhle kulungele ukusetshenziswa.Ukwenza izingubo zezingane, izingubo zabesifazane noma amabhulukwe.Ngokuvamile ububanzi bendwangu ye-twill esiyisebenzisayo ukwenza izingubo buyi-147CM.Ngenxa yezinto zikakotini, indwangu ye-cotton twill inokumunca kahle kakhulu umswakama kanye nokungena komoya.Ngesikhathi esifanayo, ingaphezulu lendwangu kakotini ye-twill igcwele, ngakho-ke ngokuvamile igezwa ngamanzi.Indwangu ye-cotton twill ngeke inciphe.Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukotini we-twill unokuminyana okuphezulu kune-plain weave, ukusetshenziswa kwentambo ephezulu kanye nokumelana okuhle nokugqokwa, ngakho-ke uthandwa kakhulu ngabantu.Indwangu ye-twill weave nayo iminyene kune-plain weave, futhi ukuthungwa kwe-three-dimensional ye-tissue kunamandla kunaleyo ye-plain weave.Kubukeka kusezingeni eliphezulu

Ibandla leZanu PF selibumbe amakomidi amahlanu azakhangela ukusilela kwentuthuko ezigabeni zeMatabeleland ngenjongo yokulungisisa loludaba.
Inkokheli yebandla leli eMatabeleland, ikhokhelwa nguMnu John Nkomo, isungule amakomidi la emhlanganweni oqhutshelwe koBulawayo ngeSonto.
Amakomidi la abalisa eyezemfundo, eyezenotho, eyezempilakahle, ebona ngezamanzi kanye lebona ngezakhiwo.
Uzulu weMatabeleland uhlezi ekhala ngokusalela muva kwalezizigaba kwezentuthuko, esola ikakhulu uhulumende weZanu PF.
Ukubunjwa kwamakomidi la sokucunule kakhulu ezinye iziphathamandla zeZanu PF ezivela kwezinye izigaba ezithi ukukhangela udaba lweMandebeleni yikuphambanisa ngoba zizinengi izabelo ezisalela muva kwezentuthuko njengeMatabeleland North leSouth.
Abanye, ikakhulu abacubungula ezombusazwe bathi iZanu PF sizama ukudinga usekelo kuzulu weMatabeleland ngoba ilizwe libhekane lokhetho.
Amacele womabili eMDC ayavumelana ekuthini ngempela iMatabeleland yiyo esilelayo ukwedlula zonke izigaba zelizwe kwezentuthuko.
Okhokhela ikomidi ezacwayisisa inhlelo zenotho ezingenziwa ukuthuthisa iMatabeleland, engumphathintambo njalo obona ngezemigodi uMnu Obert Mpofu, utshele uNtungamili Nkomo weStudio 7 ukuthi injongo yabo emqoka yikuthuthukisa izigaba zeMatebeleland, hatshi ukudinga usekelo.
Ingcwethi ecubungula ezombusazwe uMnu Effie Dlela Ncube uthe kalakuthandabuza ukuthi ibandla leZanu PF selizama ukudinga usekelo kuzakhamizi zeMatabeleland ngokwethembisa ukuthuthukisa lesisigaba.

UDokotela Themba Nyoni, omunye wabasungula linhlanganiso le, onguye okade ekhokhela kuhlelo olwenziwe ngoLwesibilu eBulawayo Club, uthi kade befundisa abantu indlela ezibalulekileyo zokusebenzisa imitshina le ebizwa ngokuthi yi-Information Communication Technology.
UDokotela Nyoni uthe imitshina yama computers yikusasa yabantu ngoba yonke into eyenziwa lamhlanje ihambelana layo imitshina le.
Uphinde wathi kulabantu abacabanga ukuthi kunzima ukusebenzisa imitshina yama computers.
“Ngombono wami bakhona sibili banengi abantwana ababona engani kunzima ukufunda …”
UDokotela Nyoni ufundisa ekolitshini lemfundo ephezulu ele National University of Science and Technology.

Ngabhejwa ubhuti wami omncane kamnandi egolo.
Ngabhejwa ubhuti wami omncane, umthondo wakhe usuthe mpo waze wabuka phezulu.
Iqhanyelwe ingane kababa. Angivule amathanga kakhulu. Ngilithi qheke igolo. Abambelele abhalanse esitulweni engihleli kuso. Awu ngaze ngabhejwa ubhuti wami omncane, awubusheke umthondo ubhuti. Ngimbambe entanyeni. Ngizwe ingquza yami iwumunca wonke umthondo kabhuti ushisa uthi bhe. Siqale sifendane. “Awu bhuti.”
Awushaye umntakababa umthondo ngizwe ukuthi inkunzi le. Abhalanse, umthondo awushaye lapho kusuka khona umsunu. Yoh ngabhejwa ubhuti wami omncane! Ngimkotele ngemilenze. Afende umntaka baba edla igolo lakubo. Ngisho indoda yami uDlamini ayingibhebhi kanje.
